    categoryGroup: "Automatic Transmission Parts",
    desc: "The 700R4 and its electronic successor the 4L60E are GM's most widely used overdrive automatic transmissions. Found in millions of trucks, SUVs, and performance cars, these units are highly rebuildable and upgradeable. We stock full master rebuild kits, Sonnax hard parts upgrades, shift kits, and remanufactured torque converters for both versions.",
